{"type": "article", "id": 33830, "title": "提问：要带走一张桌子一共需要几步？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-27T23:26:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 18311, "name": "Native Union"}, {"id": 34381, "name": "Studio Yumakano"}, {"id": 34389, "name": "Netatmo"}, {"id": 34383, "name": "Nifemi Marcus-Bello"}, {"id": 34390, "name": "Phillipe Starck"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 124, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161028072625DKNgRXEmzpUfLHOo.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>U mirror by Studio Yumakano</h3><p>一点小小的改动也可以让生活中寻常小物变得好用起来，日本工作室 <a href=\"http://yumakano.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yumakano</a> 带来的这款名为 <a href=\"http://yumakano.com/works/u-mirror/?lang=ja\" rel=\"nofollow\">U</a> 的镜子就是一个典型的例子。它是一面长方形的镜子，在靠近底部的地方采用了一个半圆形的镂空设计，将背后的墙体暴露出来。设置在缺口直径处的镜面隔板不仅提供了实用的储物空间，还营造出有趣的视觉错觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610271742412hRg3mAJ94lzKYaF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174240Tn08Ick2wmzjPO9H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174240VEoBJfNt9axTkluQ.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174241rg4upc7eWkZ3hNL9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174241RNytQLfTjcYnqKA2.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tebur table by Nifemi Marcus-Bello</h3><p>为了解决传统办公桌太过沉重不便于搬运的问题，尼日利亚设计师 <a href=\"http://nmbello.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nifemi Marcus-Bello</a> 制作了这款被称作 Tebur 的木桌。Tebur 在当地豪萨语中就是桌子的意思，Marcus-Bello 在四条桌腿的顶端加入了螺丝钉，无需再借助其他工具就可以完成组装。桌面边缘的镂空部分既能当作移动时的把手，也可以在工作时用来固定电线。搬运时只要将桌腿卸下，穿过桌底的固定环，单手就能将整张桌子提起了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174220NBlHIwOgKvmJozAe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.796108\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174220ilprfjecOTCN6PIJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664552\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174220Rp4wWSFGYh1da7Dz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174221musRZ61lX0Pg5CjI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707276\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ECLIPSE by Native Union</h3><p>如果你觉得一堆电线纠结在一起的接线板实在是“辣眼睛”，恨不得把它们藏在沙发底下，<a href=\"http://www.nativeunion.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Native Union</a> 带来的 ECLIPSE 会让你改变对接线板的固有印象。设计师们在调研后发现人们虽然平均拥有六台设备，但每天都会充电的设备一般在两到三台，这让他们最终确定为 ECLIPSE 设置三条独立的电线槽，互不影响。它其实相当于一个圆形的 USB 拓展口，侧面的滑块允许你在 USB-A 和 C 两种接口间进行转换。如果你想大大方方地把它放在墙上，只要使用随设备附带的墙挂即可。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nativeunion/eclipse-say-goodbye-to-messy-cables\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 59 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174139foP0Fj4gZRqWyuKm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174139TGqgFVoA1EJb0QBN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174139cuom5KjFBROwbpNE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174140Zx6hyAKzPfJSvYIF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Troval by Fuhua Wang</h3><p>          </p><p>外出时免不了要带上各类洗漱用品，尽管不少品牌都推出了相应的旅行套装，却很难一次性满足所有需求。由意大利华裔设计师 <a href=\"http://www.fuhuadesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fuhua Wang</a> 带来的概念设计产品 <a href=\"http://www.fuhuadesign.com/troval\" rel=\"nofollow\">Troval</a> 是一套模块化的旅行工具，手柄部分由三个黑色的配件构成，顶端提供了电动牙刷和三种不同类型的剃须刀头，必要时还可以替换成一个手电筒的光源。除此之外，手柄内部还可以容纳 USB 充电线和一个充电插头，随时可以切换一个移动电源。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174324R1ZSlzB56ekUEV7A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174324TAk3sg8pNljF145Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174325CVThEBdWsKDijHke.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535833\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174324rMOG86XQ4NBqxCuL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174324Un5YbdSWR1NPcwmI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174324iUvM4BjfhH26tSlc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Smart radiator valves by Phillipe Starck &amp; Netatmo</h3><p>法国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.starck.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phillipe Starck</a> 最近与研发智能家居的初创公司 <a href=\"https://www.netatmo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Netatmo</a> 联手设计了一款<a href=\"https://www.netatmo.com/product/energy/thermostat/additional\" rel=\"nofollow\">智能散热器阀门</a>，它的安装过程相当简单，适用于现有的标准管道阀门。这个阀门与 Netatmo 此前推出的智能恒温器组成了一套完整的智能家居系统，并且与苹果的 HomeKit 平台兼容。除了远程调整温度和设置生活习惯以外，阀门本身还拥有监测是否开窗、依据室内外环境智能调节温度的功能。造型简洁的阀门本身也能很好地融入各类家居设备当中，橙色光晕更是增添了一种温暖的高科技感。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027223532qJsZFmw17iEhvS2N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619804\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610272235332et5v98g4rObSm3B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.097800\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610272235334IryOj2tEGdpmePQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.100244\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Flora by Igöo Creativo</h3><p>          </p><p>西班牙创意机构 <a href=\"http://igloocreativo.com/portfolio\" rel=\"nofollow\">Igöo Creativo</a> 最近为第 30 届韦斯卡国际戏剧与艺术博览会（<a href=\"http://www.feriadeteatroydanza.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">International Theater and Dance Fair in Huesca</a>）设计了一套以乌龟为主视觉的形象。作为一种延续，此次博览会的纪念 T 恤包装也被设计成了乌龟的模样。透过透明的“乌龟壳”，人们可以清晰地看到 T 恤上代表第 30 届的 XXX logo，让熟悉形象的与会者能很快地发现两者间的联系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174403KUwgASXVL4deB8zr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174403Wi20VgTeJjhrC6a8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174404TBHrQk5oitweqa3j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610271744044BjyaokK1n75xHmO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174404fv5F2x3ajE1zJTwU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027174403Rr1fEtjD34AUyWbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}